svg.metadata: Created by FontForge 20120731 at Wed Jul 3 14:26:32 2019 By www-data Berthold first published Akzidenz-Grotesk in 1896. The design originates from Royal Grotesk light by Ferdinand Theinhardt who also supplied the regular, medium and bold weights. Throughout the years, Berthold has expanded this extremely popular and versatile family. AG Super was developed in 1968 by Guenter Gerhard Lange and is an excellent choice for headlines. In 2001, Guenter Gerhard Lange added more weights for Berthold including Super Italic and Extra Bold italic.
